commit_message: Cleanup intermediate files. Include bam indexing.
Added new DB info to output. Major refactoring.
Added loop for processing multiple samples. Parameter changes.
Now reports p-value of the call.
Splitted variant calling into SSCS and DCS versions.
Changed wrapper interface to iterate over a samples file.
Changed to bcftools instead of VariantAnnotator (BETA).
Fixed minor bugs regarding file names.
Changed mapping and calling options. Adapted to new interface.
Added (custom) canonical refSeq list and parser. Minor refactoring.
Added splicing variants to the report.
Splitted before- and after-DS parts of the pipeline.
Fixed cleanup. Changed intermediate file names.
Added quality filtering/trimming preprocessing. Changed VarScan parameters.
